                      "fill": "#0F172A",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "BOLOGNESE.  HALF the bolognese → foil pan 1. Spaghetti tossed with EVOO → foil pan 2. 8 oz grated parm → quart bag.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.55,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12.5,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
