                      "id": "OJRge",
                      "fill": "#0F172A",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "TERIYAKI SALMON.  Salmon + broccoli → foil pan 1. Rice → foil pan 2. Teriyaki glaze (soy + honey + minced garlic) → small jar in the FRIDGE — don't freeze.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.55,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
