                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "STIR-FRY.  Stir-fried chicken + half-bag stir-fry vegetables combined → foil pan. Rice → gallon bag. Soy-garlic sauce → small container.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.55,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12.5,
