                      "fill": "#0F172A",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "OVEN ROUND 2 (M11 + M13).  POACH or BAKE 2.5 lb chicken tenderloins until 165°F internal — SHRED. SEASON 4 salmon portions with S+P+olive oil. BAKE 400°F 18–20 min. COOL + FLAKE.",
