                      "fill": "#0F172A",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "TIKKA SAUCE + BAKE (M08).  In a saucepan, SAUTÉ 1 onion + garlic. ADD 2 cans tomato sauce + 1 can tomato paste + spices. SIMMER 15 min. STIR yogurt in. Meanwhile BAKE the marinated tikka chunks at 425°F 18–20 min. COMBINE chicken + sauce + 1 can drained garbanzos.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.55,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12.5,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    }
                  ]
