                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "BURRITO FILLING (M12).  BROWN 2 lb ground beef with diced onion + garlic + S+P + garlic powder. ADD 1 can drained black beans + 1 can drained corn. MIX well.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.55,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
