                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "PAN-SEAR COD (M10).  SEASON 2 lb thawed cod with garlic powder + S+P. PAN-SEAR in avocado oil 3–4 min per side. BREAK into large flakes.",
